name: Circuit ID History
query:
SELECT
    so.name AS "Sales Order:Link/Sales Order:200",
    soi.custom_feasibility AS "Circuit ID:Link/Feasibility:200"
FROM
    `tabSales Order` AS so
LEFT JOIN
    `tabSales Order Item` AS soi
    ON soi.parent = so.name
ORDER BY
    so.creation DESC
LIMIT 1000000;
